    <lb n="6"/>τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> οὐχ <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.72"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἤλπ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ζον</lem><rdg><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ζον</rdg></app>, ὅτι <app type="editorial"><lem resp="bgu 3 p.6"><choice><corr>ἀναβαίνεις</corr><sic>αναβενω</sic></choice></lem><rdg><choice><corr>ἀναβαίνω</corr><sic>αναβενω</sic></choice></rdg></app> εἰς τὴν μητρό-

